<h4>Dream Rewards</h4>

<div id="accordion-TCDR">
	<div class="card">
		<div class="card-header" id="heading-TCDR-One">
			<button class="btn btn-link text-left text-white-space-wrap collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse-TCDR-One" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse-TCDR-One">
				Dream Rewards Program
			</button>
		</div>
		<div id="collapse-TCDR-One" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading-TCDR-One" data-parent="#accordion-TCDR">
			<div class="card-body">
				<p>IMPORTANT NOTICE:<br />We reserve the right to add to and/or change the Dream Rewards Program Terms &amp; Conditions at any time. This means, for example, that we may change the automatic rewards earned for sessions attended or purchases made, impose caps and/or fees on earning or redeeming rewards and/or cancel rewards. </p>
				<ol>
					<li>Membership in our Dream Dinners' Dream Rewards program is open to all residents of the U.S. who are 18 years of age or older.</li>
					<li>The Dream Rewards Program is available at participating Dream Dinners locations only.</li>
					<li>To enroll, you must be in a Dream Dinners store location and request enrollment through the store owner(s) or staff of the store.</li>
					<li>Dream Dinners may cancel, modify, restrict or terminate the Dream Dinners' Dream Rewards program at any time without prior notice at its sole discretion.</li>
					<li>In case of suspected fraud, misrepresentation, abuse or violation of these rules, we reserve the right to take appropriate administrative and/or legal action, including the termination of Dream Dinners' Dream Rewards Program enrollment.</li>
					<li>By agreeing to participate in the Dream Rewards Program, you agree to receive marketing information from Dream Dinners. You may request to be removed from our distribution list by contacting a local Dream Dinners location or by emailing <a href="mailto:customerservice@dreamdinners.com">customerservice@dreamdinners.com</a></li>
					<li>Your enrollment information is confidential and will be used exclusively by Dream Dinners to present rewards to you. Dream Rewards member information will not be sold or rented to any other company or 3rd party not affiliated with Dream Dinners. We reserve the right to share this information with 3rd party companies for special co-promotions in conjunction with Dream Dinners, Inc.</li>
					<li>Employees of Dream Dinners, Inc. are ineligible.</li>
					<li>Dream Dinners' preferred guests are ineligible.</li>
					<li>Members of corporate programs or group discount programs are ineligible.</li>
					<li>In the event you choose to make purchases at different Dream Dinners locations your rewards status will move with you, only if the new location is an active participant in the Dream Rewards program and the new store location agrees to honor your present reward status.</li>
					<li>Transfer of your Dream Rewards status' to a different store location is not automatic and must be arranged with the management staff at the new location.</li>
					<li>Rewards will only be earned on in-store orders placed with a Dream Dinners franchise staff member.</li>
					<li>Rewards will only be earned on purchases of minimum size or greater. Dream Dinners Menu Sampler purchases or purchase less than 36 servings are ineligible.</li>
					<li>Rewards will not be earned on sales tax, reward redemption's, prior purchases, online purchases or gift cards.</li>
					<li>Enrollees are responsible for updating account information at <a href="https://dreamdinners.com/">dreamdinners.com </a> or through direct contact with any participating Dream Dinners Store.</li>
					<li>Enrollment in the Dream Rewards Program is void if prohibited by law in the jurisdiction in which the prospective participant resides.</li>
					<li>Only the Dream Dinners Dream Rewards enrollee that has an account with Dream Dinners may earn rewards.</li>
					<li>Dream Dinners Dream Rewards have no cash value.</li>
					<li>Dream Dinners Dream Rewards are not transferable to another guest's account.</li>
					<li>Dream Rewards enrollees must attend a session and place an order in-store at least once every 45 days to maintain active enrollment.</li>
					<li>If you do not visit a Dream Dinners location and place an order while in the store within a 45 day period, your Dream Rewards account will become inactive and any accumulated rewards will expire.</li>
					<li>The Dream Rewards "100% Delayed Payment" feature results in a $1.00 charge to credit or debit cards at the time of session registration with the balance due charged 5 days prior to the session.</li>
					<li>Rewards are available for every full-paying session scheduled while in a Dream Dinners Store. Every qualified visit is tracked. The reward tier you have qualified for after each visit is the tier you will earn for the following visit.</li>
					<li>Participation in Dream Rewards program by Dream Dinners franchisees varies by Dream Dinners location.</li>
					<li>Automatic rewards must be redeemed for the session they are earned.</li>
					<li>Automatic Dream Rewards apply toward purchases of 36 to 72 servings.</li>
					<li>When an order is under 36 servings, automatic rewards do not apply.</li>
					<li>When an order is above 72 servings, automatic rewards do not apply to the order amount exceeding the 72 serving maximum.</li>
					<li>Starting with the 13th qualifying visit, Dream Rewards guests will receive continuing discounts, reflecting the best possible pricing we have to offer, not to mention, little extras only available to our Dream Rewards' guests.</li>
				</ol>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
